Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《心》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话将与小姐的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与K的友情 背叛和自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从"老师"的视角进行了描述
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二话将从原作中没有的K的视角出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描述同一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在K眼中 两人到底是怎样的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而K又为何选择了自杀这个手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 心 最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 这是前几天提过的K
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐就像是向日葵一般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}（心 冬）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能给点好脸色看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个小套间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以跟我住一间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 K先生住那间房？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间虽然窄小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能通到院子里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“老师”？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小姐爱这么叫来嘲弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是嘲弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您老是在埋头看书嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是以小姐为标准 谁都能当老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 K先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那间房很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有个旧火盆没人用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉之前到这边来和我一起烤火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 您不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷是冷 但不用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢弹琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过努力跟才能是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是遗传了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸可都跟我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人都这么啰嗦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了些粟米酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裤子破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就脱下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在捉弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你回去得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课太无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小姐她们一起生活感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人倒也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全搞不懂女人在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人从不动脑子学东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为男女要学的东西不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上没有上进心的人就是蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人若丢了人情味可就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我没人情味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可有人情味了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为我只有嘴上说得好听 修行只是装个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你今天怎么这么感情用事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是对小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能对小姐有非份之想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人只会阻碍修行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他要你这么做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他拜托的 但没要我做到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想一辈子被拴在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 你有什么烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心情该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会藐视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 母亲擅自为我定下了婚事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 给我点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是问该进还是该退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而想退你就退得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上没有上进心的人不是蠢材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是个蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真随性啊 不是你先提起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且表面上忘了 心里也是忘不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有相应的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若说觉悟 倒也不是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就说去学校 和平常一样出门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在车站等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天会晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天行李真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 今晚不用准备我的晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去修行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你春天毕业后有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是关于这个家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你最好马上开始找别的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 和新婚夫妇住一起你也不乐意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是好友 于你总也不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 小女结婚之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要瞒着你呢 交情那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他俩都害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为他们而高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时举行婚礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日程还没定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过打算等他俩一毕业就办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想送点贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我没钱 也送不出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐在骗我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩一起背叛了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去趟医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你今天有事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 小姐好像也这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不知道什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们约定私奔 所以捉弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 K
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 要是没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我早就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有一切的你定然无法想象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有些东西是无论如何也不能相让的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我的微笑 给我的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我衷心感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今年的冬天好温暖）

Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集\N跑吧！美乐斯 前篇


